snippet.title: Cars - PSP Longplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Name: Cars

Description: Put the pedal to the metal in Disney presents a Pixar film, Cars, the video game. Join Lightning McQueen as he challenges other racers in Radiator Springs or make friends eat your dust in multiplayer mode.

Release Date: June 2006
